---Switchblade---

Switchblade watches the scenery whiz by, though he can't really 
tell what he's seeing, "I'm inpressed with your aerial performance, 
Nightstrike. All that is left to test is you in battle." he swivles back 
into a sitting position, and checks the monitors. "We've almost 
arrived, fly in low and land farther down the hill from Motormaster, 
on the side not facing the CF." Switchblade orders Nightstrike.
